snippet.title: Lindsay Lohan Engaged To Fiancé Bader Shammas
snippet.description:
Lindsay Lohan is officially a bride-to-be after her boyfriend of two years got down on one knee over the weekend. The “Mean Girls” star shared photos of her incredible ring, while announcing the happy news on Instagram.
